<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī śakavatsarē rasagirikṣōṇīṁddubhi
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ssaṁyutē śrīkūrmmasya vurasthitāya ha
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rayē svapnēśvarāyāniśaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> naivēdyārtthama
<lb n="4" break="no"/>dādanaṁggasadriśaḥ prāmuṁḍasēnāpatiḥ
<lb n="5"/>tadvāṁḍōkasi paṁccamāḍakanakaṁ drōṇa
<lb n="6" break="no"/>dvayānvartthakaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Anaṁkkabhīmabhūtyai bhā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>sva<supplied reason="omitted">dācaṁ</supplied> dratārakaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> vaiṣṇavaiḥ pāla nīyaṁ ta
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ttēṣāmapi śubhaṁ yataḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavarṣaṁ
<lb n="9" break="no"/>bulu 118<unclear>7</unclear> gunēṭi mēṣa śukla 11 yu
<lb n="10"/>śukravāramuna pāramuṁḍasēnāpati
<lb n="11"/>Anaṁkkabhīmaravatudēḍaraku Āyuṣkā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>mārtthamugānu śrīkūrmmamuna<note n="465-1">The rest of the inscription is built in.</note>
</p>

